Description: SSH connection manager with integrated terminal
 sshPilot is a GTK4/libadwaita SSH connection manager with an integrated
 VTE terminal, port forwarding and tunnelling, and an SFTP file manager.
 .
 It stores connection profiles, integrates with the system keyring for
 credentials, and drives the native OpenSSH client for every connection.
